.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH DELPHI-QR 1  "delphitools-cli 0.1.0" "delphitools manual"
.SH NAME
qr \- Generate styled QR codes
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBqr\fR [\fB\-\-size\fR] [\fB\-\-fg\fR] [\fB\-\-bg\fR] [\fB\-\-logo\fR] [\fB\-\-error\-level\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIDATA\fR> 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Generate styled QR codes
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-size\fR \fI<SIZE>\fR [default: 512]

.TP
\fB\-\-fg\fR \fI<FG>\fR [default: #000000]
Foreground colour
.TP
\fB\-\-bg\fR \fI<BG>\fR [default: #ffffff]
Background colour (use "transparent" for none)
.TP
\fB\-\-logo\fR \fI<LOGO>\fR
Optional logo to overlay (PNG, centered)
.TP
\fB\-\-error\-level\fR \fI<ERROR_LEVEL>\fR [default: M]
Error correction level: L, M, Q, H (default M)
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
<\fIDATA\fR>
Data to encode
